Class ItemEntersWaterEvent

java.lang.Object
org.bukkit.event.Event
org.blackteasea.revival.Events.ItemEntersWaterEvent
public class ItemEntersWaterEvent extends org.bukkit.event.Event
This class represents an event where an item enters water in the game. It extends the Event class provided by the Bukkit API.
